Definition:<i>A. rosaefolia koheriki</i> W.125 <i>A. rosaefolia.] [Transf. use of </i>anise,<i> an aromatic plant.] Angelica </i>(??esp. <i>A. montana</i>) and/or <i>Anistome</i> spp.
